[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      99[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     100[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Key numbers from simulation-based evaluation:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     101[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - ED boarding hours reduced ~33% vs. human-only baseline
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     102[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Surgical cancellations reduced ~34%
